_sText: This is the second map I tried to make. I know the lighting's a little awkward, and any input would be great! I'm new to CS:S mapping, so I hope to learn a little here. As far as a scenario goes, you're in a desert, shooting the other team. The first photo is bombsite B, the second is the middle between spawns,and the third is site A. Again, thank you to those downloading for the support!
